{"tid":2004381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩登記 = 黃藍絲分辨器","createTime":"2020-05-06T11:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:17:03.000Z","uid":28015,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d91bd9b3dbbc7f11c94905d9d92a9b7ccea4fbb4","tid":2004381,"uid":28015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T11:54:32.000Z","msg":"好多人將口罩網既重點放左係私隱洩漏問題上<br />\n其實政府要將市民既資料俾中聯辦、建制派既話，絕對唔需要大費周章整個網仲要特登拎你consent，佢隨時隨地俾哂大陸都得<br />\n<br />\n有一樣野政府到而家都未完全掌握到，就係個人政見顏色<br />\n平時選舉一向都係不記名，雖然可以知道黃藍比例，但你投咩票就暫時無方法得知<br />\n而家佢整個網就擺到明係拎你資料嚇尻你<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你夠膽登記 = 相信政府，唔登記 = 唔相信政府</span></span><br />\n雖然呢個分類邏輯並唔係完全準確，但起碼可以更進一步categorize每個市民<br />\n將呢個measure再配埋學歷、年齡、收入等已經做到好多demographic analysis<br />\n<br />\n所以其實登唔登記都係死"},{"pid":"edb7196d8fa82580fb19f5cf3ad64452e9da1eb3","tid":2004381,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"我老豆藍屍都唔用口罩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eb7accef9dbd9a75bc20b7fffdbe0cde9d24fe","tid":2004381,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"照登記 等比人私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea692ac3fda7cd3d5299a780b4472bef977057b","tid":2004381,"uid":305518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得好撚煩唔想搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係冇口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}